#nop ===== READABILITY MODULE LOADER =====
#nop Three aliases to manage the {readability} class.
#nop Called from Lua via session_cmd — class open/read/close is atomic
#nop within each alias body (ADR 0097).

#alias {readability_load} {#class {readability} {open};#foreach {%0} {_rd_mod} {#read ttpp/readability/modules/$_rd_mod.tin};#class {readability} {close}}

#alias {readability_clear} {#class {readability} {kill}}

#alias {readability_reload} {readability_clear;readability_load {%0}}
